{"tid":1197984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文回應反送中大遊行","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:18:49.000Z","uid":6548,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fee9b68291690c35e65b671f2718b89f7da508","tid":1197984,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/ByhJ0O9l7uY/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByhJ0O9l7uY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=20fac5a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByhJ0O9l7uY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&h=2e0bc21e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/ByhJ0O9l7uY/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a>"},{"pid":"ceb1bca6b7f6be4884762e720fe524de5fb79839","tid":1197984,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.10151242056081065/10155879900406065/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fphotos%2Fa.10151242056081065%2F10155879900406065%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=bc1feafc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.10151242056081065/10155879900406065/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a304a093da495d03377a2a6428ea0f5f7d4a3478","tid":1197984,"uid":56147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"﻿<br />\n重要的國際媒體今天都在報導昨天香港的 #反送中 大遊行。全世界關注自由、民主與人權的人，也都非常關注這個大遊行，也都很支持香港人的主張。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n台灣也不例外，我們同樣支持香港人追求自由、民主與人權。自由就像空氣一樣，只會在窒息時，才會察覺它的存在。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n因此，我再次強調，一國兩制對台灣來說，是絕對不能接受的。一旦接受一國兩制，我們就會失去捍衛自由、民主與人權的權利，也會失去選擇自己未來的權利。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n我也要呼籲台灣人民繼續關注香港的發展，一起來 #撐香港，也一起來 #保衛台灣。"},{"pid":"7cdd7ca46565494db5992b94d30457ae8688eb3f","tid":1197984,"uid":3028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/22185027/gjm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F22185027%2Fgjm.jpg&h=3c023037&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}